  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2009-0934<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2009-06-09</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Prime Minister, pursuant to paragraph 11(2)(<em>a</em>) of the <em>Financial Administration Act</em>, hereby\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;(<em>a</em>) repeals Order in Council P.C. 2008-798 of April 25, 2008, effective July 1, 2009;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;(<em>b</em>) designates the Chairperson of the Indian Residential Schools Truth and Reconciliation Commission as deputy head in respect of that Commission, effective July 1, 2009; and\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;(<em>c</em>) repeals paragraph (<em>b</em>), effective July 1, 2014.\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Sur recommandation du premier ministre et en vertu de l’alinéa 11(2)<em>a</em>) de la <em>Loi sur la gestion des finances publiques</em>, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil :\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<em>\t&nbsp;a</em>) abroge le décret C.P. 2008-798 du 25 avril 2008, avec prise d’effet le 1<sup>er</sup> juillet 2009;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<em>\t&nbsp;b</em>) désigne le président de la Commission de vérité et de réconciliation relative aux pensionnats indiens comme administrateur général de cette commission, avec prise d’effet le 1<sup>er</sup> juillet 2009;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.81in;margin-right:1.50in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<em>\t&nbsp;c</em>) abroge l’alinéa <em>b</em>), avec prise d’effet le 1<sup>er</sup> juillet 2014.\n</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
